data.description: Remodeled 3 bedroom home located in the desirable neighborhood of Sherwood Oaks. The home sits on a corner lot. Upon entering the home there is formal living area that can also be used as a home office or playroom and a dining room with a dry bar.  The kitchen features Quartz countertops with counter seating and is open to an additional living area. There is a large utility room off of the breakfast area, providing plenty of space for a mudroom. The cute screened in porch can be accessed from the second living area at the back of the home.  A large primary bedroom with a walk-in closet, a guest bath, and two additional bedrooms make up the other side of the home.  Sherwood Elementary Dual Language School is located just a short drive or walk away. City Centre and Memorial City Mall are both just a 5-minute drive, offering plenty of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Zoned to Spring Forest Middle and Stratford High School.
